Prefer native Vaadin DSL over JavaScript:
- Use Vaadin components and their built-in methods
- Avoid executeJs for customizing Vaadin components
- Leverage Vaadin's declarative API
- Use Vaadin's event system instead of custom JavaScript
- Prefer Vaadin's styling system over custom CSS/JS

Only use JavaScript when absolutely necessary and no Vaadin alternative exists. 
   